-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Securing a restful ws with spring
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1. add a security filter named springSecurityFilterChain:
    - in web.xml
    or
    - create class that extends AbstractSecurityWebApplicationInitializer

 2. add spring configuration class for security to declare who can access
    the app (SecurityConfig). Define users and roles.

 3. provide Credentials to client (RestSecuredClientConfig)